name: Anchorman
description:
Height: 38cm

Interesting Fact: He once wrestled a 9 legged octopus!

Ahoy there! This Stocky little Fisherman was lost at sea when his boat capsized in a storm. He managed to see it through the cold dark and wet night, holding on to a piece of the wreckage until he was washed up ashore! He now needs a permanent residence and promises to do all of your washing up for just one small sum of £8.50!

name: Cute Burger Man!
description:
Height: 32cm                  

Favourite food: Burgers 

This Adorable little creature needs your help! He got arrested and imprisoned for being drunk and disorderly in Bangkok and cannot afford bail! Please pledge £8.oo and he can be released and will arrive at your door within 3 – 5 working days!
